216664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T20:17:13.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3455b1ff21ed62f6f1e1445b50972aa8b0185afb","tid":963683,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T23:07:31.000Z","msg":"畀外國知道獨派仲存在緊，然後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後無然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74625b9d483ae778a63f74f2bc35d1d5d1b27078","tid":963683,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T02:29:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b80b931d00d22f8e55c92bd8736900b4776c8618","tid":963683,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJfQofN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJfQofN.png&h=27366ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同泛民做既野有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但之前就不停屌泛民左膠<br />\n到自己做個時原來又一樣<br />\n隻大陸間碟關愛座hunter<br />\n話自己唔係保皇狗打手都冇人信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930df85b83fd422b8dcc5a5d1e69ccca48eb507a","tid":963683,"uid":281463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T20:49:27.000Z","msg":"一年前啲人咁柴獨派台"}]}